HEADWORD: Beden
<hw>Bed"en</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<def>The Abyssinian or Arabian ibex (<spn>Capra Nubiana</spn>). It is
probably the wild goat of the Bible.</def>⟦br⟧
